snippet.title: EAS Child Abduction Emergency (AMBER ALERT) Pearland, Texas NOAA Weather Radio +WeatherSTAR4000
snippet.description:
Child Abduction Emergency issued December 15 at 1:19AM CST by NWS Fort Worth TX

Counties: Dallas, TX; Tarrant, TX; Fannin, TX; Parker, TX; Johnson, TX; Stephens, TX; Hill, TX; Cooke, TX; Falls, TX; Limestone, TX; Collin, TX; Mills, TX; Hunt, TX; Grayson, TX; Montague, TX; Ellis, TX; Hood, TX; Hamilton, TX; Rains, TX; Anderson, TX; Coryell, TX; Delta, TX; Kaufman, TX; Henderson, TX; Bosque, TX; Navarro, TX; Lamar, TX; Young, TX; Wise, TX; Freestone, TX; Hopkins, TX; Leon, TX; Erath, TX; Palo Pinto, TX; Somervell, TX; Rockwall, TX; Milam, TX; Eastland, TX; Bell, TX; Lampasas, TX; Van Zandt, TX; Robertson, TX; Comanche, TX; McLennan, TX; Jack, TX; Denton, TX

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THE PEARLAND POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR JAIVAN AMERE SIMPSON, BLACK, MALE, 1 YEARS OLD, 1 FOOT 6 INCHES, 22 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES. HE WAS LAST SEEN WEARING A WHITE ONESIE WITH BLUE OR BLACK SWEATPANTS.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR JADA WILLIAMS, BLACK, FEMALE, 22 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 5 INCHES, 123 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES AND WEARING EYEGLASSES WITH BLACK FRAMES, SHOULDER LENGTH HAIR, TATTOOS ON BOTH ARMS, IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION. SHE WAS LAST SEEN WEARING A GRAY OR BLACK SHIRT WITH BLACK BOTTOMS OR BLUE JEANS.

THE SUSPECT IS BELIEVED TO BE DRIVING A SILVER, 2017, HYUNDAI, ELANTRA WITH A TX TEMP TAG NUMBER OF B 6 2 9 0 G 6.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN PEARLAND, TX.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER.

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE PEARLAND POLICE DEPARTMENT.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS PEARLAND POLICE DEPARTMENT AT (281) 997-4186.
